    {
      "id": 51595,
      "post_number": 24,
      "username": "ACDC",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/e68b1a/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-09-10T12:55:23.048Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ti e di mire se keto uragane skane te bejne fare me ndryshimet klimatarike.<br>\nMos perdorni fatkeqesite natyrore per politike.<br>\nHapi kartat e uraganeve dhe te termeteve dhe do te shohesh qe edhe ku vit eshte njesoj si te tjeret,thjesht te tjeret kane rene ne oqean dhe keta nuk e kane marre kthesen sic nuk e mori Katrina dhe te tjere para Katrines.<br>\nNe 1906 San Francisko u rrafshua fare nga termeti dhe ne ate kohe nuk kishte kaq shume makina.</p>\n<p>Lexoni pak cthote shkenca e oqeanografise dhe mos merrni vetem numurat qe ju interesojne juve,por lexojini cdo gje ne kontekst.</p>\n<p>Keshtu eshte kur futen politikanet dhe gazetaret atje ku nuk marrin vesh.</p>\n<p>Sic e thashe 500 vjet ne oqeanografi jane si 1 sekonde ne jeten tone dhe marzhi I gabimit eshte shume i madh per konceptin tone per kohen dhe normal per ata qe merren me oqeanografi.</p>\n<p>Pasojat e veprimeve tona,do t ndihen pas 80-220 vjetesh ne rastin me te afert dhe 500 vjetesh ne rast se flasim per marzh gabimi normal.</p>\n<p>Shiko se cfare flet ky perfaqesuesi I Hollivudit per Teksasin qe eshte zemra dhe hambari i Amerikes.<br>\nVazhdoni keshtu se Shtepine e Bardhe keni per ta pare me dylbi…Liberalet jane njesoj si fashistet.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"http://thehill.com/misc/favicon.ico\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n      <a href=\"http://thehill.com/homenews/media/349942-bill-maher-unfair-for-states-like-texas-to-request-federal-assistance-after?amp\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"03:41PM - 09 September 2017\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">TheHill – 9 Sep 17</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:645/363;\"><img src=\"http://thehill.com/sites/default/files/blogs/maherbill_072812getty_1.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"http://thehill.com/homenews/media/349942-bill-maher-unfair-for-states-like-texas-to-request-federal-assistance-after?amp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bill Maher: 'Unfair' for states like Texas to request federal aid after Harvey</a></h3>\n\n<p>HBO host Bill Maher complained that it \"seems a little unfair\" for residents of conservative states like Texas to rely on federal assistance in the wake of Hurricane Harvey.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
