hingtonpost.com/rf/image_1484w/2010-2019/WashingtonPost/2017/09/08/Editorial-Opinion/Images/Nevada_Senate_Race_05b3b-NLKD.jpg?t=20170517\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/did-lesbians-cause-hurricanes-irma-and-harvey-god-knows/2017/09/08/638efbca-94bf-11e7-89fa-bb822a46da5b_story.html?utm_term=.7a87860ded38\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Opinion | Did lesbians cause Hurricanes Irma and Harvey? God knows.</a></h3>\n\n<p>It’s irresponsible to say God is directing weather patterns to make political statements. But let’s do it anyway.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
